parameters.name: CreateTimeFrom
parameters.description: The earliest time when the data quality monitor starts to run.

parameters.name: CreateTimeTo
parameters.description: The latest time when the data quality monitor starts to run.

parameters.name: DataQualityScanId
parameters.description: The ID of the data quality monitor.

parameters.name: Filter
parameters.description:
The extended query filter. Supported parameters:

*   TaskInstanceId

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the results. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of records per page. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: SortBy
parameters.description:
The list of sorting fields. Supports fields such as last modified time and creation time. Format: "SortField+SortOrder (Desc/Asc)", where Asc is the default. Valid values:

*   CreateTime (Desc/Asc)
*   Id (Desc/Asc)

parameters.name: Status
parameters.description:
The status of the data quality check result.

*   Pass
*   Running
*   Error
*   Fail
*   Warn
